name_pretty: Google Cloud Bigquery Migration V2alpha API
ruby-cloud-description: google-cloud-bigquery-migration-v2alpha is the official client library for the Google Cloud Bigquery Migration V2alpha API. Note that google-cloud-bigquery-migration-v2alpha is a version-specific client library. For most uses, we recommend installing the main client library google-cloud-bigquery-migration instead. See the readme for more details.
